
Documentation via zzso of the healing of zzso lateral collateral ankle ligaments after functional zzso 

35 patients with ankle zzso were examined by zzso and stress zzso 13 were operated afterwards, 22 patients underwent a functional conservative therapy and were examined by zzso and stress zzso and second time after three zzso 

zzso reports were correct in 12 of 13 operated zzso After conservative therapy we did not find any disrupted ankle zzso zzso showed intact ligaments thickened by zzso 

zzso is able to show injuries of the lateral collateral ankle ligaments and demonstrates the healing by zzso after conservative zzso 

